  <brief_title>Impact of Diet and/or Exercise-Induced Weight Loss on Cardiovascular Risk Factors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Longitudinal Impact of Diet and/or Exercise-Induced Weight Loss on Metabolic Markers of Cardiovascular Disease</official_title>
